       Name: Redemption
    Classes: Cleric(15)
   Duration: N/A
   Modifies: N/A
       Type: Defensive
Description: This spell allows the caster to restore life back into a fallen
             player. A raised player will be healed for an amount of health,
             mana, and moves relative to the caster's level. They will also
             regain some of their experience lost through death.
